    <title>babyrasterizer-手写软光栅化渲染器踩坑记</title>
    <link href="https://pan64271.github.io/2021/03/22/babyrasterizer-%E6%89%8B%E5%86%99%E8%BD%AF%E5%85%89%E6%A0%85%E5%8C%96%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%E5%99%A8%E8%B8%A9%E5%9D%91%E8%AE%B0/"/>
